### Phase 2: Edge Function updater (Deno tests)

**2.1 Extend existing test suite:** `supabase/functions/update-lead-status/lead_status_updater.test.ts`

Add test cases for agency owner ownership:

```typescript
// Around line 200+ (after existing ownership tests)

Deno.test("update: agency owner can update agent lead", async () => {
  const owner_id = "owner-uuid";
  const agent_id = "agent-uuid";
  const lead_id = "lead-123";

  const fake = make_fake_client({
    leads: [
      { id: lead_id, agent_id, status: "new" },
    ],
  });

  // Configure fake to simulate RLS: owner can SELECT via can_edit_lead
  // (in real DB, the SELECT would succeed because is_agency_owner_of returns true)
  const updater = make_lead_status_updater(fake);

  const result = await updater.update({
    user_id: owner_id,  // caller is owner, not agent
    lead_id,
    new_status: "contacted",
  });

  assert(result.ok, "Agency owner should be able to update agent lead");
  assertEquals(result.lead?.status, "contacted");
});

Deno.test("update: owner from different agency cannot update", async () => {
  const other_owner_id = "other-owner-uuid";
  const agent_id = "agent-uuid";
  const lead_id = "lead-123";

  const fake = make_fake_client({
    leads: [
      { id: lead_id, agent_id, status: "new" },
    ],
  });

  // Configure fake to simulate RLS: other_owner CANNOT SELECT (RLS filters it)
  fake.configure_rls_filter((caller_id, row) => {
    // Simulate: only agent or their agency owner can see/edit
    return row.agent_id === caller_id; // other_owner_id doesn't match
  });

  const updater = make_lead_status_updater(fake);

  const result = await updater.update({
    user_id: other_owner_id,
    lead_id,
    new_status: "contacted",
  });

  assert(!result.ok, "Owner from different agency should be unauthorized");
  assertEquals(result.error_code, "UNAUTHORIZED_AGENT");
});
```

**Note:** The fake client needs to simulate RLS behavior. If the current fake doesn't support this, extend it to accept a filter function that mimics the `can_edit_lead` logic.

**Run:**
